title: Maruti Suzuki's total sales increase 5% to 1,68,089 units in April
description: Maruti Suzuki India's April sales rose by 4.7% to 1,68,089 units. Domestic sales of various vehicle segments fluctuated compared to last year, while exports increased to 22,160 units.
